  <description>
    <p>
      Kega Fusion is an emulator for a number of different Sega 8 and 16-bit consoles.
    </p>
    <p>
      <li>Emulates the Sega SG-1000, SC-3000, Master System, and Game Gear</li>
      <li>Emulates the Sega MegaDrive/Genesis and its accessories the Sega Mega-CD/Sega-CD and the Sega 32X</li>
      <li>Emulates the Sega Pico</li>
    </p>
  </description>
